# Curate the Core Memory Canon

## Question

Layer 1 of the briefing answer: a small curated set of core-memory pages
(principles, vision lines, standing law — files-are-truth, gates-never-
default, secrets-never-persist, no-opaque-spinners, .svx law, refuse-loudly)
that COMPILES into dark-wizard graft blocks so every agent on the fleet
carries them fused in its system prompt. Decide with Joel: the initial
canon list (one breath to read), the source location
(dark-wizard/.brain/core-memories/?), the compile step (graft-block
generation from svx), and the promotion path (reflector monthly promotion
proposes; Joel accepts). HITL — the canon is Joel's voice.
